00:00:00,156 --> 00:00:02,486
Lola has been working with me for over 2 years.

2
00:00:02,666 --> 00:00:06,226
She has 4 of her children living with her and is often preoccupied

3
00:00:06,226 --> 00:00:08,086
with their issues when she comes to work.

4
00:00:08,466 --> 00:00:11,926
She does the best she can when she's here, but she's always complaining

5
00:00:11,926 --> 00:00:14,636
about how much work she has to do at home with her kids.

6
00:00:15,006 --> 00:00:19,126
She talks about how hard it is to 'run' two households since she also works for me.

7
00:00:19,426 --> 00:00:23,506
A couple of times I've even heard her mutter that I should consider myself lucky

8
00:00:23,506 --> 00:00:27,266
to have her helping me, because not everyone can get help at home like I do.

